PLACEHOLDER — Previously Published Data Source
This file contains a single molecular time-calibrated consensus phylogeny for birds (Jetz et al. 2012; BirdTree).
It is used to calculate Evolutionary Distinctiveness (ED) scores and as the covariance structure in PGLS models.
Download the original phylogeny from:
[LINK TO BE FILLED IN]
Place the downloaded file in this directory as singe_bird_phylo.tre before running FuDGE_clean.Rmd.
